    "IntroductionThe emergence of generative AI models has transformed the landscape of artificial intelligence significantly [1][2][3][4][5].",
    "Spearheading this evolution are two pioneering language models (LLMs): ChatGPT and Google Gemini [6][7][8].",
    "Both platforms showcase unprecedented capabilities in engaging in nuanced conversations, crafting intricate textual compositions, and generating diverse creative content types [9][10][11][12].",
    "These abilities hold immense promise for businesses, promising to revolutionize various facets of operations [13,14].",
    "Understanding the distinctive merits and limitations of these LLMs will be crucial in gauging the effectiveness of generative AI in business management settings."
